data.description: Welcome to your ideal home in the heart of North Port! This inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence features a practical split floor plan for ultimate comfort and convenience. With a newer roof, a recently inspected septic and public water, set your worries aside!     Picture yourself in a home that caters to your everyday needs, with a His and Hers shower adding a touch of functionality to your daily routine. Plus, with schools just a short 5 to 12-minute drive away, your family's daily activities are easily accessible.    This home is designed for your lifestyle with extra covered parking on the side, providing protection for your vehicles. For your loved ones, an outside shower with a charming stone walkway makes outdoor playtime a breeze.    Storage is never an issue here, thanks to additional cabinets in the garage and a convenient laundry sink. Stay organized effortlessly in this thoughtfully designed space.    Nestled in a quiet neighborhood without HOA fees or deed restrictions, enjoy the freedom to bring your pets and your boat. This is your haven, where you set the rules!    Discover the ease of living in North Port, with this home strategically located close to schools, restaurants, shopping, golf courses, gulf beaches, and more. Seize the opportunity to make this practical property your own. Act quickly, as homes like these are in high demand. Your ideal lifestyle awaits!
